{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十五章“死巷”中，伪装成大主顾的王万武来到杂货店，借买空货物逼张老实交出老板。铁震天从声音认出旧敌，警告马如龙小心。王万武以分筋错骨手和大力鹰爪功成名，却被貌似老实的张老实一招制住，双臂关节被拧断。惨败后的王万武在屋内认出铁震天，坦白十年前曾因愧疚而出卖并借刀杀他。张老实的真实身份更显神秘，马如龙冲出店外，却发现原本热闹的巷子已空无一人，成了死巷。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "我们这家杂货店不能算太大，也不能算太小，店里的货不能算太多，也不能算太少，你一个人能全部搬得走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "大主顾",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我可以叫人来搬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "大主顾",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "只要你开出价钱，我就付，就去叫人来搬东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "我只不过是这杂货店里的伙计，这么大的生意，我做不了主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "大主顾",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "谁能做主？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "我们的老板。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "大主顾",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你们的老板在不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "就在里面，你可以进去问他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "大主顾",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我不进去，你叫他出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "你为什么不进去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "大主顾",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "他为什么不出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "因为他是老板，不管是大老板，还是小老板，多多少少都有点架子的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "大主顾",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "他不出来，我什么都不买。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "现在你不买也不行了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "所以你非进去不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "王万武！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "小心你那伙计的两条手臂。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个人是谁！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个人是谁？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你那个伙计究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你……你在这里。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "你本来就应该知道我在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我知道你在这里，我到这里来，就是为了想要你的命，因为我对不起你，出卖过你，所以我反而更恨你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "十年前，我出卖了你，就因为那时我已经做过对不起你的事，生怕你知道，所以，才想借别人的刀来杀你。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我宁愿死在你的手里，那时你若杀了我，我也不会有今天了。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    }
  ],
